Okay this is the exact same map as bhop_underground, though this one is much better.. 

Upgrades in this map:

- Clear sky 
- Lighter
- New textures
- Added a bonus lvl
- Added option to walk around the map on "top"

-- People are saying this is so much better than the other one, and i have to agree.. And thats the reason why it got a new name and im uploading it to fpsbanana..

--- The difficulty of this map is about Medium.

Enjoy !
